.\"Note, however,
.\"that if
.\".I uucp
.\"is compiled with the
.\".B \-DSMALL
.\"option,
.\"there will be very little debugging output.
..
.PP
This program is typically started by the shell \f2uudemon.cleanup\f1,
which should be started by
.IR cron (1M).
.SH FILES
.PD 0
.TP 20
/usr/lib/uucp
directory with commands used by
.I uucleanup
internally
.TP
/var/spool/uucp
spool directory
.PD
.SH SEE ALSO
cron(1M),
uucp(1C),
uux(1C).
